$PROB THEOPHYLLINE ORAL $INPUT ID AMT TIME DV BWT $DATA ../THEO.CSV $PRED DOSE = 320 KA = THETA(1) * EXP(ETA(1)) V = THETA(2) * EXP(ETA(2)) K = THETA(3) * EXP(ETA(3))
F = DOSE / V * KA / (KA - K) * (EXP(-K*TIME) - EXP(-KA*TIME)) Y = F + F * EPS(1) + EPS(2)
$THETA (0, 2) (0, 50) (0, 0.1)
$OMEGA BLOCK(3) 0.2 0.1 0.2 0.1 0.1 0.2
$SIGMA 0.1 0.1
$EST MAX=9999 NOTBT NOOBT NOSBT NOABORT METHOD=COND LAPL INTER $COV PRINT=ERS $TAB ID ETA(1) ETA(2) ETA(3) FIRSTONLY NOAPPEND FILE=INDIPARA.OUT $TAB ID AMT TIME BWT ONEHEADER FILE=FIT.OUT
